Comment: 0,0:19:56.14,0:20:01.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,【插曲 海賊之歌】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正時間和地點都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂 調大音量拚了命放！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸…宰了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 小千秋好可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認數據！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能光聽歌什麼都不做…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告機動戰艦大十字號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間為午後0點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點參見附件的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜露死苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,by 海賊船弁天丸船長 加藤茉莉香及——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有私掠船許可證的海賊小伙伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜露死苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方好像回應了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來解析！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}躲起來 給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}如果讓我發現你們 就把你們打殘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}即便你們聯合起來 勝利也屬於我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}贏了後的香檳最為甘甜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待的不得了我一直在大笑著停不下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大十字艦長 克沃茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然心眼很壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就得這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發動機輸出功率穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在處於最好的狀態！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感測器也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥系統沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓對方見識見識海賊之魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,title
